# Description:
#  README file for package psana-tools
#------------------------------------------------------------------------

Package author: David A. Schneider

Brief description:
==================
Testing and diagnostic tools. Scripts for maintaining and manage test data.

Detailed description:
=====================

Package includes the psana module dump, run as

psana -m psana_test.dump datasource

This is a DDL generated Python Psana module that dumps everything from 
the data source. See the confluence page 

https://confluence.slac.stanford.edu/display/PSDM/psana+-+Module+Catalog

where a detailed description lives.

It also includes the command line tool

xtclinedump

to look at xtc files. Run the program for the help message.

Finally it includes the script

psana_test/src/psanaTestLib.py

for running regression tests, and managing test data.
The internal confluence page

https://confluence.slac.stanford.edu/display/PCDS/Psana_test+package

includes more information.

